      *@설정상태 1 - 전체, 2 - 설정, 3 - 미설정, 4 - 당월도래
           EVALUATE XDJL4107-I-STUP-STUS
      *@설정상태가전체인경우
               WHEN CO-CHA-1
      *@SQLIO OPEN
                    PERFORM S3210-XQJL1071-OPEN-RTN
                       THRU S3210-XQJL1071-OPEN-EXT
                    MOVE CO-CHA-Y
                      TO WK-BIT
      *@SQL FETCH
                    PERFORM UNTIL WK-BIT     = CO-CHA-N OR
                                  WK-CUR-CNT = CO-MAX-CNT
      *@데이터를　읽음(FETCH)
                            PERFORM S3220-XQJL1071-FETCH-RTN
                               THRU S3220-XQJL1071-FETCH-EXT
                    END-PERFORM
      *@SQLIO CLOSE
                    PERFORM S3230-XQJL1071-CLOSE-RTN
                       THRU S3230-XQJL1071-CLOSE-EXT
161024*@설정상태가 2:설정 4:당월도래 인경우
               WHEN CO-CHA-2
               WHEN CO-CHA-4
      *@SQLIO OPEN
                    PERFORM S3240-XQJL1072-OPEN-RTN
                       THRU S3240-XQJL1072-OPEN-EXT
                    MOVE CO-CHA-Y
                      TO WK-BIT
      *@SQLIO FETCH
                    PERFORM UNTIL WK-BIT     = CO-CHA-N OR
                                  WK-CUR-CNT = CO-MAX-CNT
      *@데이터를　읽음(FETCH)
                            PERFORM S3250-XQJL1072-FETCH-RTN
                               THRU S3250-XQJL1072-FETCH-EXT
