               WHEN CO-CHA-3
      *@SQLIO OPEN
                    PERFORM S3270-XQJL1073-OPEN-RTN
                       THRU S3270-XQJL1073-OPEN-EXT
                    MOVE CO-CHA-Y
                      TO WK-BIT
      *@SQLIO FETCH
                    PERFORM UNTIL WK-BIT     = CO-CHA-N OR
                                  WK-CUR-CNT = CO-MAX-CNT
      *@ 데이터를　읽음(FETCH)
                            PERFORM S3280-XQJL1073-FETCH-RTN
                               THRU S3280-XQJL1073-FETCH-EXT
                    END-PERFORM

      *@SQLIO CLOSE
